
Alpha is a open-source real time strategy game engine. It is written in C#,
using the OpenGL and SDL libraries.

Alpha is available under the GNU GPL, please see COPYING file for details.

For more information about Alpha itself go to http://alpha.devnet.ro/

To build alpha see http://alpha.devnet.ro/wiki/Compiling . In short, on an
unix machine all you need is opengl, sdl and mono. Building goes like:

    ./Extras/CreateMakefile.sh
    make

